        <h4>Stretch</h4>
        <p>We make our jeans to last. We are 
        proud of their durability and you’ll 
        surely notice the stiffness when first 
        put them on. They should be real snug, 
        and even difficult to button.  But don’t 
        worry, within a wear or two, you’ll start 
        to notice a bit of loosening. This is part 
        of the normal breaking in process with any 
        selvage jean, and part of the fun.  Our jeans 
        will stretch as much as 1 whole size. If that 
        is too much for you, just put them in warm or 
        hot water and they will shrink back up.
        </p>
