        <p>Part of the what makes selvage jeans interesting
        is the way that the color will develop based 
        on your wear, habits and style. That is the 
        main reason we advise you to not wash them 
        for a good while. The longer you go, the more 
        pronounced the fading will be in all the right 
        spots. Typically, this is in the thigh, knee, back 
        pocket and anywhere else that has seen some distress.
